We encourage you to share as many of your thoughts on anything and anyone in the game as you’re comfortable with! This is a place for people to see a log of your journey from day 1 to final tribal council. Right now, the only people who have access to viewing your confessionals are members of Production, and our Hungry Specs! Hungry Specs are all vetted & trusted individuals in the community, so you don’t have to worry about any leaks. If you want to make sure ONLY members of production can see a message, you should use your submissions channel instead. That channel will also be used for challenge submissions.
